This brand new freestanding building includes the following features:
* 5,500sqm of high bay warehouse
* 299sqm of quality corporate office over two levels
* Large hardstand area - ideal for storage and container set down areas
* 9,822sqm land area
* Loading dock
* Awning area approx 246sqm
* Superb semi and B double access

The Wacol Industrial Estate is located at the southern end of Viking Drive with uninterrupted exposure to the Ipswich Motorway. Wacol is located at the western end of the Logan Motorway at the junction with the Ipswich Motorway, providing excellent arterial road connection throughout metropolitan Brisbane and South East Qld. This region is only 15klms South West of the Brisbane CBD and within the established Western Brisbane Industrial precinct.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents.

This superb facility is currently under construction with Practical Completion due mid 2013. This facility will suit large logistics and warehouse users who require a quality, high bay, well located, sprinklered warehouse. Features of the building includes:
* 11,742sqm high bay warehouse
* 504sqm carpeted and air conditioned office
* 8 level grade roller doors
* 4 loading docks
* ESFR Sprinkler System
* B Double Access
* Ample carparks provided
* 10m minimum internal clearance
* 10 metre awnings

Features of the site include:
- 50sqm Office
- 700sqm Warehouse area
- 3,103sqm General Industry land
- Large concrete hardstand areas
- Spray booth onsite (negotiable)

Located in Wacol's highly sought after industrial precinct this freestanding site offers direct access to the Ipswich, Logan and Centenary Motorways.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Mark Gilbride of CBRE.

Features of the property include:

- 700sqm Warehouse
- 50sqm Office
- 3,100sqm General Industry land
- Large hardstand area
- Multiple roller door access
- Ample car parking
- Good internal height

This property is located on Quindus Street only 16 radial kilometres from the CBD and offers convenient access to the Ipswich and Logan Motorways.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents from CBRE.

Features of the site include:
- 100sqm Office area (additional offices onsite if required)
- 950sqm Warehouse area
- 600sqm Awning & workshop
- 4,264sqm General Industry land
- Large overhead gantry crane
- Three phase power supply
- Dual crossovers off Formation Street

A highly exposed site that benefits from direct access to the Ipswich and Logan Motorways. Wacol is a sought after Industrial precinct located in the Western Corridor.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Mark Gilbride the Exclusive Agent.

CBRE are pleased to offer 39 McRoyle Street, Wacol to the market for Sale or Lease. This is a rare opportunity to secure a large manufacturing facility in the heart of Wacol.

Features of the property include:
+ 3,650sqm Warehouse area 
+ 480sqm Office & showroom over two levels 
+ 16,190sqm General Industry site 
+ 3 x 10T Gantry cranes (7m under hook) 
+ Over 8,000sqm of hardstand areas 
+ Large three phase power supply 
+ Multiple container height roller doors
+ Fully secured site with drive around capabilities 
+ Ample onsite hardstand for container set down & truck turning 

The property offers immediate access to the Ipswich, Centenary and Logan Motorways, as well as other adjoining arterials. Wacol is a highly sought after Industrial precinct located within Brisbane's Western Corridor.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Mark Gilbride of CBRE.
